KA-Lite - https://learningequality.org/ka-lite/ 
"An offline version of Khan Academy.
A free lightweight solution providing high-quality education where you need it most. 
Bringing the power of online learning to the offline world."


Installation Docs - http://ka-lite.readthedocs.io/en/0.16.x/installguide/install_main.html


sudo apt-get install python-m2crypto python-pkg-resources nginx python-psutil
sudo wget https://learningequality.org/r/deb-pi-installer-0-17 --no-check-certificate --content-disposition
sudo dpkg -i ka-lite-raspberry-pi*.deb

kalite manage setup

Videos go into /home/pi/.kalite/content
